{"tid":1678933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本澀谷有人者戴上習近平面具慶祝萬聖節","createTime":"2019-10-28T02:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T12:56:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":128,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"61dec3d55be7576035ba962c4e1e6624e1032bbc","tid":1678933,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/10/26/phpnwkGv0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F10%2F26%2FphpnwkGv0.jpg&h=25710760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷取自umbrella.movement.exhibition＠FB）<br />\n<br />\n萬聖節將至，日本東京澀谷出現奇景，約有100名在日香港人在今晚（26日）發起「100 Poohs 㷫萬聖節」（㷫字在粵語有熱、生氣及激動之意），戴著習近平面具上街拍照，吸引眾人目光。<br />\n<br />\n一名網友在臉書發起「100 Poohs 㷫萬聖節」活動，邀請人們戴著習近平面具，26日晚間7點在澀谷知名地標八公像前集合拍照，並組成人鏈，來回通過澀谷的大型十字路口，聲援香港示威。<br />\n<br />\n照片中，許多人戴著習近平面具，其中，一名參加者全身穿上小熊維尼的衣服，同時抱著一隻維尼玩偶，相當吸睛。<br />\n<br />\n活動要求參加者發揮創意，扮裝成「習習」，穿著抗爭標語上衣，不過禁止舉牌、舉旗、喊口號或唱歌，並呼籲大家將照片傳至社交平台時，記得寫下「#StandwiththePooh」標籤。<br />\n<br />\n臉書粉專「香港雨傘運動展」表示，今天的澀谷出現相當驚人的光景，值得慶幸的是，雖然警方繃緊神經，不過活動沒有受到任何人的妨礙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/10/26/phpWeFcCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F10%2F26%2FphpWeFcCD.jpg&h=02bce849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷取自umbrella.movement.exhibition＠FB）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2958514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2958514&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4ab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=3f370c48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2958514&h=33feec80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2958514</a>"},{"pid":"67aeed3880892d19374e5cea490970966dbeff0d","tid":1678933,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"78ff615bbdab0f5701091a50e12134f57422a36a","tid":1678933,"uid":226421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"sick play<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1813a4cddb47d9e214b7457ffdedafa489e4d107","tid":1678933,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65ec2f1daec1dffa5e5a48cd489f6c9603791db","tid":1678933,"uid":295865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:12:54.000Z","msg":"真係要 Tweet 出國際"},{"pid":"0d06695f70d1fd7defebe858624848dee0cc8f0b","tid":1678933,"uid":72630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"香港學唔學呢招？"},{"pid":"6250af07d367a16fd719bf97584853a21d1aa321","tid":1678933,"uid":203797,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"日本咁多支蝗<br />\n呢啲時候又唔出聲？<br />\n唔係好愛國？<br />\n淨係識恃強凌弱 畫花人個繪馬都要靜靜雞"},{"pid":"2ba0098868257ea8f24bde4c2b08312e3b9f94a6","tid":1678933,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6250af07d367a16fd719bf97584853a21d1aa321","tid":1678933,"uid":203797,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"日本咁多支蝗<br />\n呢啲時候又唔出聲？<br />\n唔係好愛國？<br />\n淨係識恃強凌弱 畫花人個繪馬都要靜靜雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:40:32.000Z","msg":"只愛國不愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33132460cc1302d011233a5ac7448daf3d1e638b","tid":1678933,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc